    <subfield code="y">00001 \footnotesize (Color online) (Upper) Y/Y($^{12}C$) as a function of A for even-even isotopes with I = 0. (Middle) Same as the upper, but for odd-odd isotopes with I=0. (Bottom) The pairing energy term corrected yields for isotopes with I=0. The lines are the results fitted by $A^{-\tau}$. The extracted $\tau$ values are shown in each figure.</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="856" ind1="4" ind2=" ">
